msgstr "अनुरोध प्राप्त भयो!"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_success.html:5
msgid ""
"Thanks — a Gaamos representative will contact you within one business day."
msgstr "धन्यवाद — Gaamos प्रतिनिधिले एक कार्य दिनभित्र तपाईंलाई सम्पर्क गर्नेछन्।"

#: templates/marketing/_contact_success.html:7
