msgid "Features"
msgstr "सुविधाहरू"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:5
msgid "Everything a busy venue needs. Nothing it doesn't."
msgstr "व्यस्त स्थललाई चाहिने सबै कुरा। नचाहिने केही पनि होइन।"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:11
msgid "Menu Builder"
msgstr "मेनु बिल्डर"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:12
msgid "Build your menu in minutes, not weekends"
msgstr "मेनु मिनेटमै बनाउनुहोस्, हप्तौं होइन"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:13
msgid ""
"Start from a global library of dishes and drinks — tick the ones you serve, "
"drop them into categories, set your prices, add photos. Your menu is live "
"before your coffee gets cold."
msgstr ""
"परिकार र पेय पदार्थको साझा लाइब्रेरीबाट सुरु गर्नुहोस् — आफूले बेच्ने छान्नुहोस्, "
"श्रेणीहरूमा राख्नुहोस्, मूल्य तोक्नुहोस्, फोटो थप्नुहोस्। कफी सेलाउनुअघि नै तपाईंको मेनु "
"लाइभ हुन्छ।"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:15
msgid "Template library of ready-made items"
msgstr "तयार आइटमहरूको टेम्प्लेट लाइब्रेरी"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:16
msgid "Drag-and-drop categories and groups"
msgstr "तानेर राख्न मिल्ने श्रेणी र समूह"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:17
msgid "Clone a menu from another branch in one tap"
msgstr "एक ट्यापमै अर्को शाखाको मेनु कपी गर्नुहोस्"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:22
msgid "· 10 items"
msgstr "· 10 आइटम"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:23
msgid "live"
msgstr "लाइभ"

#: templates/marketing/_features.html:30
msgid "+ Add from library"
